title: Coffee consumption in the U.S. 2013/14 - 2018/19
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags, containing a total of 6 data points.
In general Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags has rose over the Year.

Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags is roughly constant from 2013/2014 to 2014/2015, slightly increasing from 2014/2015 to 2015/2016, roughly constant from 2015/2016 to 2016/2017, and finally slightly increasing from 2016/2017 to 2018/2019.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014/2015 and 2015/2016.
The highest Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags, of value 26.5 was reached at Year 2018/2019
The lowest Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags, of value 23.58 was reported at Year 2014/2015
